title: "Industrial building" means a building or part thereof wherein products or material are fabricated,
clause_text: "Industrial building" means a building or part thereof wherein products or material are fabricated, assembled or processed, such as assembly plants, laboratories, power plants, refineries, gas plants, mills, dairies and factories
